      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>立方體的柱頭於低處以圓弧角度過渡為圓形立柱，常見於中世紀建築。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
